pages.text: Yeah it's that time again. I finally managed to figure out what caused the issues I had with updating my private test server. Thank you Minecraft for being so horrible at what you're are. Now that I finally figured that out, I'm able to release a fix for it. Once that is done. I may continue working in the v2.3.0 version of the pack.

So fingers crossed.
Thanks again for keep playing my modpack! I hope you're having a great time.
Sincerely Enderman
